We provide a helper method which aims to make plotting indicators simple. For further information on the charting API please see our Charting section.

private Breakaway _breakaway;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_breakaway = Breakaway(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_breakaway.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "Breakaway Period", _breakaway.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "Breakaway Current", _breakaway.Current);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.breakaway = self.Breakaway(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.breakaway.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "Breakaway Period", self.breakaway.Period)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "Breakaway Current", self.breakaway.Current)
